The paper deals with the study of loss rates of predictors in the online prediction framework, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of game theory in the paper suggests that it could also be categorized under cs.GT. The paper also discusses convergence properties and ergodic theorems, which are topics related to dynamical systems (cs.DS) and control theory (cs.SY).
